{"tid":2061205,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[晴報] 【復課壓力】復課後追進度功課量增　家長學童壓力大︰親子關係再次緊張","createTime":"2020-06-12T08:17:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-12T09:08:21.000Z","uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"15462fce276711906452912a8c8f700fc2b7b209","tid":2061205,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T08:17:41.000Z","msg":"[晴報] 【復課壓力】復課後追進度功課量增 家長學童壓力大︰親子關係再次緊張<br />\n 14:27 2020/06/12 <br />\n<br />\n朋友苦笑說︰「復課前，多了帶孩子到公園玩樂，親子關係良好；復課後，忙於指導孩子完成功課，協助讀書溫習，親子關係又再次緊張起來。」<br />\n<br />\n當老師有追趕進度的壓力時，從前用多天來完成的課題，現在只能用一、兩天便要完成它；從前可以用多些活動和互動，讓不同能力的同學從活動中學習，從參與中了解和認知，現在老師只能以較直接和快捷的方式向學生灌輸知識。<br />\n<br />\n(已節錄)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://skypost.ulifestyle.com.hk/column/article/2668246/%E5%BE%A9%E8%AA%B2%E5%BE%8C%E7%9A%84%E8%BF%BD%E8%B6%95\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fskypost.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fcolumn%2Farticle%2F2668246%2F%25E5%25BE%25A9%25E8%25AA%25B2%25E5%25BE%258C%25E7%259A%2584%25E8%25BF%25BD%25E8%25B6%2595&d=q8peb0UcLz3Z6%2FQAtnUTjBVTfDkzAunSCULMKrq9Td0%3D&h=83cdaaad\" target=\"_blank\">https://skypost.ulifestyle.com.hk/column/article/2668246/%E5%BE%A9%E8%AA%B2%E5%BE%8C%E7%9A%84%E8%BF%BD%E8%B6%95</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">停課的後遺症真大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"02b651033fb39327938871a64b504194a65dbf73","tid":2061205,"uid":25468,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T08:19:30.000Z","msg":"晴報啲小說就咪撚 post 啦"},{"pid":"7418725ec08bd46a0804f5c94e753b56af389b3d","tid":2061205,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"02b651033fb39327938871a64b504194a65dbf73","tid":2061205,"uid":25468,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T08:19:30.000Z","msg":"晴報啲小說就咪撚 post 啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T08:26:39.000Z","msg":"你同香討果班一見到蘋果貼文就話假新聞的網軍無分別"},{"pid":"f35947a831635ae765ebb43dc0